[a list of patches for 2.3.10, with the hopes that they will
be applied to 2.3.11]
There's a couple of buglets with applying the 2.3.10 patches
to 2.3.11;  I had a little bugfix for loop.c in that was 
also discovered by other people, so that patch rejects, and,
more importantly, the include file for setup.c is rejected.
This version of the same patch is explicitly against 2.3.11;
